item.title: Ambassador HTB Walkthrough
item.author: emdwyer
item.description: Intro This was my first medium difficulty box. I noticed it was the highest rated and due to be retired in 2 days – so I decided to tackle this machine in order to quickly release a walkthrough (content creation! clicks! views!) and practice my note taking skills. While I enjoy being in ’the zone’, it is well worthwhile breaking momentarily to take comprehensive notes that can be weaved into a cohesive narrative – if only so I can retrace my steps and help with future CTF challenges.
